1. Introduction
Welcome to DailyCash Book - Offline ("App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our mobile application. By using this App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
2. Information Collection and Use
We DO NOT collect, store, or share any personal information.
DailyCash Book - Offline is a 100% offline application that works entirely on your device. All data you enter (expenses, income, transactions) is stored locally on your device only and is never transmitted to our servers or shared with any third parties.
3. Data Storage
Local Storage Only: All your financial data, transactions, and records are stored locally on your device's internal storage
No Cloud Sync: We do not upload, backup, or sync your data to any cloud servers
No Internet Required: The app functions completely offline without requiring an internet connection
Your Data, Your Control: You have complete control over your data. You can export, delete, or backup your data at any time
4. Permissions
The app may request the following permissions:
Storage Permission (READ/WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE)
Purpose: To save and export your cash book data, reports, and backups to your device storage
Usage: Only used when you choose to export or backup your data
Data Access: Limited to app-specific folders only
Other Permissions
No other permissions are required for core app functionality
5. Third-Party Services
We do NOT use any third-party services that collect data:
❌ No Analytics SDKs (Google Analytics, Firebase, etc.)
❌ No Advertising Networks (AdMob, Facebook Ads, etc.)
❌ No Crash Reporting Tools
❌ No Social Media Integration
6. Children's Privacy
Our App is a general-purpose financial tool and does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13.
7. Data Security
Since all data is stored locally on your device:
We implement no server-side security measures (as there are no servers)
Your device's security (PIN, pattern, fingerprint) protects your data
We recommend regularly backing up your data using the app's export feature
